text.tspan: One patron can give extra, which benefits
a project overall, but the matching tapers off.

flowRoot.flowPara: With all patrons at 1-share, your input has a nearly 1:1 matching effect from the other patrons.
With a double pledge (2 shares), you count like 2 patrons, and effective matching is slightly reduced (because you are also matching yourself)
It takes another doubling to 4 shares, to count like 3 patrons for matching
Although your own donation grows with more patrons joining, each additional unit you add is itself matched many times over.
It takes 8 shares to count like 4 patrons for matching.
And 16 shares counts like 5 patrons for matching,
